Resource Profile: Radiotherapy Plan

Official URL: https://build.fhir.org/ig/arkhn/arkhn-ig-osiris/StructureDefinition/radiotherapy-plan Version: 2.1.0
Active as of 2023-04-06 Computable Name: RadiotherapyPlan

Radiotherapy plans planned or delivered to a patient

Usage:
